      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:5:3:119:7",
      "text": [
        " قَالَ رَسُولُ اللَّهِ ( صلى الله عليه وآله ) أَيُّمَا امْرَأَةٍ حُرَّةٍ زَوَّجَتْ نَفْسَهَا عَبْداً بِغَيْرِ إِذْنِ مَوْلَاهُ فَقَدْ أَبَاحَتْ فَرْجَهَا وَ لَا صَدَاقَ لَهَا ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Al Nowfaly, from Al Sakuny, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Rasool-Allah<sup>saww</sup> said: ‘Whichever free woman marries herself to a slave without a permission of his master, so she has legalized her private parts and there is no dower for her’."
        ]
      }
    },
